snippet.title: Logicked
snippet.description:
Entertaining responses to bad arguments, with a focus on religion.

All content is protected under DMCA Fair Use.

I make no claim to being a scientist, philosopher, historian, mathematician, astrophotographer, journalist, wine expert, golf champion, or space marine. I am a self-educated layman and these videos are partially a learning tool. If I make a claim, double-check it before you take it as fact. I'm as fallible as anyone and there are a few known errors in my videos. But my arguments and reasoning stand or fall on their own merits.
